
Ranger Help for: enemy insect
=============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing insect means your Ranger specializes against ants, beetles,
wasps, mosquitoes, mantises, and other many-legged chitinous creatures.

This is a broad choice across forests, swamps, deserts, jungles, beaches,
mountains, and underground spaces.

COMMAND:
  setenemy insect

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
